~~Compromise solution", Maghreb Review 01, 2- 3( 5891 ): 15- 65; G.
~~Ayache," Aspects de la crise financie? re au Maroc apre? s l'e? xpe?
~~dition espagnole de 0681", in Etudes d'histoire marocaine) Rabat, 3891
